### ① 一覧取得(最初は空っぽのはず)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books

### ② 本を登録
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "わかるJava入門",
  "author": "田中太郎",
  "publishedYear": 2021,
  "read": false
}

### ③ 一覧取得(登録した本が増えてるはず)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books

### ④ 詳細取得(idは③の結果を見て書き換えてね)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/1

### ⑤ 更新
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/books/5
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "わかるJava入門",
  "author": "田中太郎",
  "publishedYear": 2021,
  "read": true
}

### ⑥ 削除
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/books/5

### バリデーションNGパターン(タイトル空文字)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "author": "テスト著者",
  "publishedYear": 2020,
  "read": false
}

### バリデーションNGパターン(出版年がマイナス)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "テストタイトル",
  "author": "テスト著者",
  "publishedYear": -5,
  "read": false
}

### バリデーションOKパターン(正常な登録)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "正常なタイトル",
  "author": "正常な著者",
  "publishedYear": 2023,
  "read": false
}